153 (2) streaming entertainment operators that fail to submit remuneration of the assessment
154 within sixty (60) days of the aforestated deadline shall be assessed a penalty equal to three
155 percent (3%) of the gross revenues derived from, or pertaining to, the sale or provision of
156 streaming entertainment service to individuals and businesses in the Commonwealth during the
157 applicable time period;
158 (3) any monetary penalty assessed upon a streaming entertainment operator for failure to
